CONFIG
==================================================

agent.yaml can now include:
  registry_path: /path/to/judge-loop/registry

Env override: JUDGE_REGISTRY_PATH
Default: ./registry  (relative to CWD — works from repo root)

==================================================
DESIGN NOTES
==================================================

Local bundle (not HTTP download):
  The registry files live in the repo under registry/.
  The sync reads from disk — no external network calls for the registry itself.
  Future: RegistryPath could point to a cloned remote registry repo.

Track manifests not synced as problems:
  Tracks are ordering/curation data, not problem metadata.
  LoadAllProblems skips tracks/ and roadmaps/ — only providers/ have ProblemManifest.
  Track data is not yet stored in DB (future milestone: track management API).

Idempotent sync:
  UpsertFromManifest uses ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE — safe to run repeatedly.
  registry_versions gets a new row each sync (append-only audit trail).

Test cases NOT in registry:
  The registry is metadata-only (no problem statements, no test cases).
  The 25 seeded problems have sample test cases from seed_problems.sql.
  Future: provider-specific test case scripts or ICPC-style judge input files.

==================================================
WHAT'S NOT DONE (intentional)
==================================================

- Track/roadmap data not stored in DB (future)
- Remote registry HTTP fetch (future — currently disk-only)
- Checksum validation (sha256 field is placeholder "sha256:local")
- Conflict detection based on version field (upserts unconditionally)
- Test cases in registry manifests (out of scope per design)

